{"word":"H2691 - חָצֵר - châtsêr - khaw-tsare' - Court","slug":"H2691","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">חָצֵר</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>châtsêr"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>khaw-tsare'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Court"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05D7;&#x05E6;&#x05E8; - cha&#x0302;tse&#x0302;r</b> - <i>khaw-tsare'</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/H2690\">H2690</a> in its original sense; a <i>yard</i> (as <i>inclosed</i> by a fence); also a <i>hamlet</i> (as similarly <i>surrounded</i> with walls): - court, tower, village."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H2674\">H2674</a>, <a href=\"#/H2675\">H2675</a>, <a href=\"#/H2681\">H2681</a>, <a href=\"#/H2692\">H2692</a>, <a href=\"#/H2693\">H2693</a>, <a href=\"#/H2694\">H2694</a>, <a href=\"#/H2695\">H2695</a>, <a href=\"#/H2696\">H2696</a>, <a href=\"#/H2697\">H2697</a>, <a href=\"#/H2698\">H2698</a>, <a href=\"#/H2699\">H2699</a>, <a href=\"#/H2700\">H2700</a>, <a href=\"#/H2701\">H2701</a>, <a href=\"#/H2702\">H2702</a>, <a href=\"#/H2703\">H2703</a>, <a href=\"#/H2704\">H2704</a>, <a href=\"#/H2705\">H2705</a>"}]}